@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_enwbah(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.63 + tmp + 0.69)) / wp.cos(wp.sin(tmp + 0.97)))
    v0 = wp.cos((0.97 - wp.exp(v2 + 0.64)))
    v1 = v2
    v0 = ((v1 - (v0 + 0.58 / tmp + 0.89)) / (0.98 - wp.abs(v1 + 0.18)))
    tmp = wp.sin(v0)
    v2 = tmp
    v0 = (v2 + wp.abs(1.00))
    data[tid] = v0
